venue.name: Pavilion at Nevers Park

item.description:
Picnic for Haiti, August 11th Nevers Park 12 -5 p.m.
The event is coordinated by another organization that asked us to have a booth there to support them. The event is to raise money for a school in Haiti.  We will have our general Jaycee information, wapping fair promotion and kids games. 

We need a few people to staff the booth and assist with games.
item.name: Haiti Picnic booth
